***************************************
*                                     *
*    Tango icon theme for PDFEdit     *
*                                     *
******************* by mischamajskij **

1) INSTALLATION - USE

To install unpack the archive into ~/.pdfedit/icon or (as root) into <prefix>/share/pdfedit/icon, where <prefix> can be "/usr", "/usr/local" or other, depending on your installation

To choose the theme go to Tools > Options > Look and Feel, select Tango and restart the program.


This application icon theme was created by Tiziano Mattei using existing icons from various Tango sets; some icons have been re-assembled or drawn from scratch. The later are licensed under CC-BY-SA, the remaining ones are either under the same license or GPL.

